headline: Take-Two (TTWO): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q1 Earnings?
summary: Take-Two has had an impressive run over the past six months as its shares have beaten the S&P 500 by 22.2%. The stock now trades at $233.91, marking a 26.3% gain. This performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
